INSERT INTO `Company` VALUES (23,54,'jpeg','https://www.wework.com/locations/new-york-city/charging-bull/','WeWork - Charging Bull','<p>WeWork is the largest coworking franchise with locations and a community extending around the globe. Their Charging Bull location is nestled in the historic hub of Wall Street - surrounded by scenic views and gorgeous buildings. Tenants typically select this location if they\'re commuting from downtown Manhattan or Brooklyn, or if they\'re looking to keep a tight budget. The Charging Bull location is less expensive than its northern Manhattan counterparts.</p>\r\n<p><strong><em>Pricing Starting A</em>t:</strong>&nbsp;Desk - $550/mo; Private Office - $1300/mo</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',2,1,'WeWork - Charging Bull'),(24,61,'jpeg','https://www.wework.com/locations/new-york-city/nomad/','WeWork - Nomad','<p>WeWork Nomad is anchored in the center of Manhattan just north of Madison Square Park. With Members that range from early stage startups to more established companies, this is the perfect community to start or grow your business.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><em>Pricing Starting At</em>:&nbsp;</strong>Desk - $450/mo; Private Office - $750/mo</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',2,1,'WeWork - Nomad'),(25,65,'jpeg','https://www.wework.com/locations/new-york-city/west-broadway/','WeWork - West Broadway','<p>Bright, beautiful, and historic, WeWork West Broadway is an elegant loft-style building in the heart of Soho.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><em>Pricing Starting At</em></strong>: Private Office - $950</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',NULL,1,'WeWork - West Broadway'),(36,53,'png','https://www.wework.com/locations/new-york-city/bryant-park/','WeWork - Bryant Park','<p>This building is just a short walk from iconic New York locations like Time Square and Grand Central, members are only steps away from the tranquility of Bryant Park. Positioned in one of the city\'s most dynamic neighborhoods, this location is a compelling space to grow your business.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><em>Pricing Starting A</em>t:</strong> Desk - $500/mo; Private Office - $1000/mo</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',2,1,'WeWork - Bryant Park'),(32,63,'png','https://www.wework.com/locations/new-york-city/soho/','WeWork - Soho','<p>The historic brick building in Soho is where it all began, playing host to the first WeWork community at intersection of Soho, Nolita, Little Italy and Chinatown. The space continues to provide a collaborative enviroment with frequent events and resources all designed to make members here more successful.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><em>Pricing Starting At</em>:</strong> Desk - $400/mo; Private Office - $750/mo</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',1,1,'WeWork - Soho'),(33,62,'png','https://www.wework.com/locations/new-york-city/park-south/','WeWork - Park South','<p>WeWork Park South is beautifully designed with a warm, inviting aesthetic located in a rich corridor for business and technology. This space includes fun amenities like an arcade room, lounges, and an internal staircase so it\'s members can always connect.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><em>Pricing Starting At</em></strong>: Private Office - $700/mo</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',NULL,1,'WeWork - Park South'),(39,56,'png','https://www.wework.com/locations/new-york-city/empire-state/','WeWork - Empire State','<p>In addition to being centrally located in one of Manhattan\'s busiest commercial districts right across from&nbsp;the&nbsp;iconic New York City&nbsp;Landmark. WeWork Empire State offers members creative resources,&nbsp;like their&nbsp;recording studio and screening room.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><em>Pricing Starting At</em>:</strong> Desk - $500; Private Office - $700/mo</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',NULL,1,'WeWork - Empire State'),(35,60,'png','https://www.wework.com/locations/new-york-city/meatpacking/','WeWork - Meatpacking','<p>The location\'s beautiful, warm aesthetic complements the formerly gritty and now trendy Meatpacking District. Members can walk the nearby High Line park and West Village during the day, while indulging in some of the city\'s top restaurants and bars at night.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><em><strong>Pricing Starting At:</strong></em> Desk - $600/mo; Private Office - $800/mo&nbsp;</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',NULL,1,'WeWork - Meatpacking'),(37,57,'png','https://www.wework.com/locations/new-york-city/fulton-center/','WeWork - Fulton Center','<p>Lower Manhattan, often called the world\'s financial capital, is rapidly evolving into a hub of new media and technology companies. Members in this location admire unobstructed views of New York that may look familiar. Gordon Gekko\'s office from the 1987 film Wall Street is on the 23rd floor of this high-rise, which is now one of WeWork\'s premiere event spaces. Standing above the Fulton Center transit hub, this unique space is accessible from anywhere.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><em>Pricing Starting At</em>:</strong> Desk - $450/mo; Private Office - $750/mo</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',NULL,1,'WeWork - Fulton Center'),(38,59,'png','https://www.wework.com/locations/new-york-city/madison/','WeWork - Madison','<p>Just a few blocks from Grand Central Station, classic New York meets new world ambition in this coveted location on Madison Avenue, which features a convenient market that offers healthy snacks and drinks to it\'s members.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><em>Pricing Starting At</em>:</strong> Desk - $550/mo; Private Office - $650&nbsp;</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',NULL,1,'WeWork - Madison'),(40,64,'png','https://www.wework.com/locations/new-york-city/soho-west/','WeWork - Soho West','<p>Once called the Printing District, Soho West is home to media and advertising giants, digital innovators and tech startups. The community working out of this revived industrial-style building can enjoy the 28-seat screening room and form relationships with a large, diverse group of entrepreneurs.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><em>Pricing Starting At</em>:</strong> Desk - $400/mo; Private Office - $700/mo</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',NULL,1,'WeWork - Soho West'),(41,55,'jpeg','https://www.wework.com/locations/new-york-city/dumbo/','WeWork - Dumbo COMING SOON!','<p>WeWork is the community of creators. They transform buildings into beautiful collaborative workspaces and provide infrastructure, services, events and technology so their members can focus on doing what they love.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><em>Pricing Starting At: </em></strong>Varies<strong><br /></strong></p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',NULL,1,'WeWork - Dumbo'),(53,45,'png','http://workattheyard.com/','The Yard - Lincoln Square','<p>Just blocks from Lincoln Center, Central Park, and Columbus Circle, this brand-new&nbsp;Upper West Side space&nbsp;features month-to-month office rentals including conference rooms, kitchens, and reception services.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><strong><em>Pricing Starting At</em>:</strong> Open Desk Coworking - $500/mo; Private Office $800/mo&nbsp;</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',1,1,'The Yard - Lincoln Square'),(96,3,'jpeg','http://www.alleynyc.com/','Alley NYC - NoMad COMING SOON!','<div style=\"widows: auto; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: #777777; font-family: lato, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; widows: auto;\">AlleyNYC\'s flagship location will be a 36,000 square-foot space at 119-125 W 24th St. AlleyNYC is a dynamic coworking space. Their fully equipped space features all of the usual office stuff (desks, comfy chairs, WiFi, flat screens, printers, conference/board rooms, a stocked kitchen) plus a dope atmosphere where come of the most innovative entrepreneurs come to collaborate every day.</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"widows: auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; text-shadow: none;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: lato, arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #777777;\"><em style=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit;\"><strong style=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit;\">Pricing Starting&nbsp;At:</strong></em>&nbsp;$450/mo</span></span></span></div>\r\n</div>','coworking@trumanjames.com',1,1,'Alley NYC - NoMad'),(43,37,'png','http://www.techspace.com/spaces/new-york/union-square/','TechSpace - Union Square','<p>TechSpace Union Square is New York&rsquo;s premier office space work environment that provides the ideal solution for companies seeking flexible office space. This office space is located in the heart of Silicon Alley in New York and encompasses three floors with over 60,000 square-feet of premium real estate. Their Union Square facility boasts 104 office suites and 585 workspaces to support your growing business needs.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><em>Pricing Starting At:</em></strong>&nbsp;Varies</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',NULL,1,'TechSpace - Union Square'),(44,38,'png','http://www.techspace.com/spaces/new-york/west-village/','TechSpace - NoMad','<p>TechSpace NoMad, located in an energetic Manhattan hotspot, is New York\'s premier office space work environment that provides the ideal solution for companies seeking flexible office space. This Manhattan space encompasses two floors with over 23,000 square-feet of premium real estate. Our NoMad facility features 62 office suites and 207 workspaces to support your growing business needs.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><em><strong>Pricing Starting At:</strong></em><strong>&nbsp;</strong>Varies</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',1,1,'TechSpace - NoMad'),(45,36,'png','http://www.techspace.com/spaces/new-york/flatiron/','TechSpace - Flatiron','<p>TechSpace Flatiron, the latest New York location offers 22 fully private offices and suites with 172 seats in the sought after neighborhood of Flatiron, offering close proximity for all that midtown south has to offer.&nbsp; This incredible office space boasts an exclusive roof-top deck as well as a first of its kind penthouse suite.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><em><strong>Pricing Starting At:</strong></em><strong>&nbsp;</strong>Varies</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',1,1,'TechSpace - Flatiron'),(46,66,'png','http://www.workhousenyc.com/gallery','WorkHouse NYC','<p>The coworking space is located in a 15-story commercial building. It is only two blocks from the Rockefeller Center. The building has a roof deck and usable terraces, robust technology infrastructure, and lots of natural light. At 21 West 46th Street, tenants will find high ceilings, concrete floors, steel sash windows, co-working lounge with phone booths, private meeting rooms, event space, full kitchens, and fully equipped conference rooms and lounge areas.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><em><strong>Pricing Starting At:</strong>&nbsp;</em>Desk - $450/mo; Private Office - $1,500/mo</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',5,1,'WorkHouse NYC'),(47,14,'jpeg','http://www.empireoffices.com/gallery-galleria.shtml','Empire Offices - Galleria','<p>Located in one of Manhattan\'s most desirable locations&ndash;57th &amp; Park Avenue&ndash;the Galleria offers clients an elegant corporate environment and prestigious business address. Occupying nearly 20,000 square feet of the 10th &amp; 11th floors, clients have access to their modern and innovative private offices which accommodate anywhere from one to ten people. Common areas include an upscale reception area with flat screen television and seven-story indoor atrium with seating.</p>\r\n<p><strong><em>Pricing Starting At:</em></strong><em>&nbsp;</em>Varies</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',NULL,1,'Empire Offices - Galleria'),(48,15,'jpeg','http://www.empireoffices.com/floorplans-grandcentral.shtml','Empire Offices - Grand Central','<p>Located in one of Manhattan&rsquo;s most prestigious locations &mdash; 41st Street &amp; Madison Avenue &mdash; their Grand Central is a custom designed office center. Each office has a wall mounted, cable ready, LCD television. Offices are furnished with Knoll desks and Herman Miller Aeron Chairs. The impressive reception area is bright and contemporary in style. The center features TouchDown Space, a large Strategy Room and a large and beautifully appointed Meeting Room. Common areas include a kitchen area with seating and a LCD TV.</p>\r\n<p><em><strong>Pricing Starting At:</strong></em><strong>&nbsp;</strong>Varies</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',NULL,1,'Empire Offices - Grand Central'),(49,16,'png','http://www.empireoffices.com/floorplans-worklofts.shtml','Empire Offices - Work Lofts','<p>Situated across from Battery Park and adjacent to the Ritz Carlton Hotel, the Work Lofts at Battery offer a highly visible and accessible downtown location. The frescoed ceiling and elegant marble floors mark one of Manhattans most impressively designed lobby entrances. Detailed paintings give way to the office center\'s innovative and bold style that showcases varying shapes, colors and materials&ndash;all creating a signature office environment. Work Lofts floor plans are as innovative and modern as the common areas. Empire Work Lofts, open plan, loft like spaces offers a range of space options, from one-person workstations to large Empire Offices featuring built-in conference rooms. Work Lofts are designed for flexibility and equipped with the latest in technology. Modular furniture allows clients to create a truly unique and customized space.</p>\r\n<p><em><strong>Pricing Starting At:</strong></em><strong>&nbsp;</strong>Varies</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',NULL,1,'Empire Offices - Work Lofts'),(50,13,'png','http://www.empireoffices.com/midtown-manhattan-office-space.shtml','Empire Offices - Fifth Ave','<p>Located in one of Manhattan\'s most recognizable locations - 44th Street &amp; 5th Avenue - Empire Fifth Avenue is a creatively designed office center. Each office has a wall mounted, cable ready, LED television. Offices are furnished with Knoll desks and Herman Miller Aeron Chairs. The impressive reception area is bright and contemporary in style. The Midtown Manhattan office space center features TouchDown Space, multiple Strategy Rooms and a large and beautifully appointed Meeting Room. Common areas include a kitchen area with seating and equipped with a LED TV. A fully equipped business lounge is another unique feature of Empire Fifth Avenue\'s executive suites. 535 Fifth Avenue is just steps away from Grand Central Station.</p>\r\n<p><strong><em>Pricing Starting At</em>:</strong>&nbsp;Varies</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',NULL,1,'Empire Offices - Fifth Ave'),(51,2,'png','http://www.alleynyc.com/','Alley NYC','<p>AlleyNYC is a 16,000 square foot entrepreneurial hub right in Silicon Alley, where teams and individuals can grow there businesses surrounded by like minded people, and work collaboratively in a supportive environment. Their members take advantage of outstanding networking opportunities and special events hosted by &lsquo;The Alley&rsquo;, such as speaker series with Angel Investors and experienced entrepreneurs, as well as hackathons, free happy hours (twice a week), yoga sessions and massages! Their aim is to help start-ups bridge the gap between their innovative ideas and stable business establishment</p>\r\n<p><strong><em>Pricing Starting At</em>:</strong> Desk - $450/mo; Private Office - $2,220/mo&nbsp;</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',3,1,'Alley NYC - Midtown West'),(52,41,'png','http://fueled.com/coworking-space-nyc/#companies','The Fueled Collective','<p style=\"text-align: left;\">The Fueled Collective is a co-working space in Manhattan that has grown into a family of 20 of the most exciting startups in NYC. At the collective, we share a love of plush leather couches, year round ice cream, and ping pong tournaments, not to mention, amazing views of lower Manhattan and a killer snack bar!&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><em>Pricing Starting At</em>:</strong> Desk - $800/mo</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',NULL,1,'The Fueled Collective'),(54,43,'png','http://workattheyard.com/','The Yard - Flatiron','<p>Their newest location at 234 5th Avenue. Four floors flooded with natural light, this Flatiron-NoMad location features 88 private office suites and coworking lounges with convenient access to Midtown, Chelsea, Union Square, and Madison Square Park.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><strong><em>Pricing Starting At:</em> </strong>Desk - $450/mo; Private Office - $800/mo</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',2,1,'The Yard - Flatiron'),(55,44,'png','http://workattheyard.com/','The Yard - LES','<p>This&nbsp;downtown office space features a private state-of-the-art rooftop with outdoor lounge, indoor desks, and office suites with private terraces. Combining classic Lower East Side style with architect David Bers modern design, this space is conveniently located just steps from the Williamsburg Bridge, East Village, Chinatown, and Soho.</p>\r\n<p><em><strong>Pricing Starting At:</strong> </em>Desk - $395/mo; Private Office - $650/mo&nbsp;</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',1,1,'The Yard - LES'),(56,46,'png','http://workattheyard.com/','The Yard - Williamsburg','<p>The Yard&rsquo;s flagship space combines open areas with private work spaces in a converted factory overlooking McCarren Park. All spaces have natural light, serene ambience, and access to amenities including conference rooms, private lounge, kitchen, bike storage, and high-speed internet. Walking distance from the L and G trains in Williamsburg and Greenpoint.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><strong><em>Pricing Starting At</em>:</strong> Desk - $225/mo; Private Office - $475/mo</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',NULL,1,'The Yard - Williamsburg'),(57,25,'png','http://joynture.com/','Joynture','<p>Located in the famous Bank of New York Building in Manhattan\'s Financial District, Joynture is part of a recent tech movement revitalizing the old banking districts with vibrant technologists. FiDi is home to the South Street Seaport, some of the best food trucks in NY, and abundant shopping. The BNY Building is centrally located to most metro area subway lines.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><strong><em>Pricing Starting At</em>:</strong> Desk - $500/mo&nbsp;</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',NULL,1,'Joynture'),(58,29,'png','http://nwc.co/','New Work City','<p class=\"p1\">The 4,700 square foot interior features shared desks, meeting rooms, couches and work lighting. Interested workers are welcome to just show up and find a space to work! From internet to printers and monitors, 412 Broadway has all the essentials for coworking and is designed for workers comfortable with an environment that buzzes with excitement and energy.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><strong><em>Pricing Starting At</em></strong>: Desk - $375/mo</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',1,1,'New Work City'),(59,22,'png','http://www.green-desk.com/','Green Desk - Williamsburg','<p class=\"p1\">Williamsburg is an influential hub for indie rock, hipster culture, and the local art community. 240 Kent Ave is located on the Williamsburg water front.&nbsp;The building is a mix of retail on the ground floor, offices on the 2nd and 3rd floor and event space on the rooftop.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><strong><em>Pricing Starting At</em>:</strong> Desk - $299/mo; Private Office - $425/mo&nbsp;</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',NULL,1,'Green Desk - Williamsburg'),(60,20,'png','http://www.green-desk.com/','Green Desk - Greenpoint','<p class=\"p1\">The Greenpoint location is right on the Brooklyn Water Front. Just 3 blocks off the G train and a short walk to the new East River Ferry, this space is easily accessible. Greenpoint is quickly becoming a popular spot for new businesses due to its\' diversity. Built in the 1800s and utilized as a rope factory for many years, this historical building is one of the last to display wood sidewalks surrounding it. In 2011, the space was renovated to transform the interior into a flexible office space.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><strong><em>Pricing Starting At</em>:</strong> Desk - $299/mo; Private Office - $425/mo&nbsp;</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',NULL,1,'Green Desk - Greenpoint'),(61,18,'png','http://www.green-desk.com/','Green Desk - Downtown Brooklyn','<p class=\"p1\">Centrally located next to almost all of Brooklyn Subway lines including&nbsp;A,B, C,Q,R,2,3,4,5 this is the most convenient&nbsp;location for your clients to travel to.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><strong><em>Pricing Starting At</em>:</strong> Desk - $299/mo; Private Office - $425/mo</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',NULL,1,'Green Desk - Downtown Brooklyn'),(62,19,'png','http://www.green-desk.com/','Green Desk - Dumbo','<p class=\"p1\">Views of the city on the north side and over looking the DUMBO triangle park on the south side, 155 Water has windows all around.&nbsp;Dumbo is home to 25 percent of New York City-based tech firms. Within a 10-block radius are 500 tech and creative firms that employ over 10,000 people.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"p3\"><strong><em>Pricing Starting At</em>:</strong> Desk - $299/mo; Private Office - $425/mo&nbsp;</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',NULL,1,'Green Desk - Dumbo'),(63,21,'png','http://www.green-desk.com/','Green Desk - LIC','<p class=\"p1\">Now open: located&nbsp;across&nbsp;the street from the subway on Northern Blvd in the center of Long&nbsp;Island business district.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"p3\"><strong><em>Pricing Starting At</em>:</strong> Desk - $299/mo; Private Office - $425/mo&nbsp;</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',NULL,1,'Green Desk - LIC'),(64,6,'png','http://cowork.rs/','Cowork|Rs - Flatiron','<p>Located at 115 East 23rd Street in Flatiron - COWORK|RS offers you a ready-made community with the potential for collaborations with dynamic people working on cool projects. The organizational setup takes care of the practical stuff&ndash;so you don&rsquo;t have to. The space is bright and comfortable, and makes challenging work easy and fun. The layout encourages random conversation between members to spark ideas, solve problems and collaborate. Their staff works directly with members to support your business needs and make important connections.</p>\r\n<p><em><strong>Pricing Starting At:</strong></em><strong>&nbsp;</strong>Desk - $450/mo Desk; Private Office - $700/mo Office</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',3,1,'Cowork|Rs'),(65,11,'png','https://www.emerge212.com/3C-details.html','Emerge 212 - Columbus Circle','<p>Prominently situated at one of the city\'s most vibrant locations at the crossroads of culture and commerce, 3 Columbus Circle has rapidly transformed into a renowned symbol of business. This reimagined tower boasts a sleek glass curtain wall, a new entrance and canopy, each contributing to a commanding power, focus and presence. 3 Columbus Circle offers efficient, flexible floor layouts, and boasting views sweeping Central Park and Manhattan&rsquo;s business center.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><em><strong>Pricing Starting</strong><strong> At:</strong></em><strong>&nbsp;</strong>Private Office -&nbsp;$1,650/mo</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',NULL,1,'Emerge 212 - Columbus Circle'),(66,12,'png','https://www.emerge212.com/Park-details.html','Emerge 212 - Park Ave','<p>Prominently situated at one of the city\'s most vibrant locations, 125 Park is a 25 story office building located in the Grand Central District of Midtown Manhattan. This center is a high-end contemporary-style executive business center, ideal for expanding and transitional businesses. Impress your clients from the moment they enter the lobby, featuring new marble floors finished with Italian Balsatina stone highlighted with vaulted ceilings finished with Venetian plaster.</p>\r\n<p><em><strong>Pricing Starting</strong><strong>&nbsp;At:</strong></em><strong>&nbsp;</strong>Private Office -&nbsp;$1,650/mo</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',NULL,1,'Emerge 212 - Park Ave'),(67,10,'png','https://www.emerge212.com/28-details.html','Emerge 212 - 44th Street','<p>At 28 West 44th Street is located between 5<span class=\"s1\">th</span> and 6<span class=\"s1\">th</span> Avenues, in a vibrant, sophisticated neighborhood between Bryant Park and Times Square. Built in 1919, the 23-story landmarked building offers entrances on both 43rd and 44th Streets. The main floor features a convenient retail arcade and an elegant, renovated lobby encased in Botticino marble with travertine flooring and mahogany-paneled elevators.</p>\r\n<p><em><strong>Pricing Starting</strong><strong>&nbsp;At:</strong></em><strong>&nbsp;</strong>Private Office -&nbsp;$1,650/mo</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',NULL,1,'Emerge 212 - 44th Street'),(68,8,'png','http://www.districtcowork.com/','District Cowork','<p>District NoMad is Silicon Alley&rsquo;s newest entrant. Located in the center of Manhattan, on Broadway between 29th and 30th, close to all forms of transportation, we offer Members a social and energetic vibe coupled with the best elements of a workspace designed to foster both professional success and personal well-being.</p>\r\n<p><strong><em>Pricing Starting At:</em></strong>&nbsp;Desk - $500/mo; Private Office - Varies</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',NULL,1,'District Cowork'),(69,17,'png','http://letsensemble.com/','Ensemble','<p>Located at 1150 Avenue of the Americas, the property has been rated by Time Out New York Magazine as one of the city&rsquo;s coolest coworking spaces. Ensemble draws a lot of tech and startup companies. In a like-minded work environment, individuals can collaborate, network, and frequently bounce off ideas with one another.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><em><strong>Pricing Starting At:</strong></em> Desk - $450/mo; Private Office - $4,500</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',1,1,'Ensemble'),(71,4,'png','http://www.center4nyc.org/overview/','Center4','<p>Situated in New York&rsquo;s Garment District, Center4 operates its coworking rental space out of 205 West 39th Street. For tenants looking for a collaborative environment in the Times Square area, this is a great option. Amenities at 205 West 39th Street include a lounge area, a kitchen, coffee station, great A/V equipment, access to all-in-one printer stations, and Center4 provides ergonomic office furniture.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><strong><em>Pricing Starting At</em></strong>: Desk - $450/mo</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',1,1,'Center4'),(72,5,'png','http://nyc.socialinnovation.org/about','Centre for Social Innovation','<p>CSI provides private offices, private desks and part-time desks&nbsp; to people on a mission. All members have 24/7 access to workspace + lounges, meeting rooms, classrooms, wifi, equipment and&mdash;most importantly&mdash;vibrant programming and a community of passionate change-makers.</p>\r\n<p><em><strong>Pricing Starting At:</strong></em>&nbsp;Non-dedicated Desk - $400; Dedicated Desk - $450; Private Office - $1,200</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',1,1,'Centre for Social Innovation'),(73,1,'png','http://www.42west24.com/','42West24','<p>This Manhattan office space lies in the midst of the lively Flatiron district, with nearby shopping, restaurants, movie theaters and art galleries. Close to Madison Square Park, several subway lines and PATH.&nbsp;<span class=\"s1\">Enjoy super-fast internet access on their giga-switched network for free. The secure card key access allows you to work on your own schedule. Conveniently book the conference room online whenever you need it.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><strong><em>Pricing Starting At</em>:</strong> Desk - $299/mo; Private Office - $1,900/mo</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',2,1,'42West24'),(74,23,'jpeg','http://ingoodcompany.com/','In Good Company','<p>Where women entrepreneurs go to work, meet &amp; learn. In Good Company is a coworking space located at 16 W 23rd Street, in New York City, New York. This low cost space offers 1500 square feet of coworking area, with 15 desks and 8 offices. Day passes are available for one time usage &amp; monthly access requires membership.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><em><strong>Pricing Starting At:</strong></em> Part-Time Desk - $150/mo; Private Office - $1,000/mo</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',1,1,'In Good Company'),(75,26,'png','http://www.microoffice.com/','Micro Office Solutions - Midtown','<p>This recently renovated space features unlimited phone usage, with lines specific for each business and individual. There is high-speed internet available to all users, whether as permanent members or for one-day use. Memberships to Micro Office Solutions offer access to 10 hours of conference room time to begin with, access to all of Micro Office&rsquo;s locations, as well as the variety of tools and equipment available: printers, projectors, organizing tools.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><strong><em>Pricing Starting At</em>:</strong> Desk - $495/mo; Private Office - $1,000/mo</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',NULL,1,'Micro Office Solutions - Midtown'),(76,27,'png','http://www.microoffice.com/','Micro Office Solutions - Time Square','<p class=\"p1\">Micro Office Solutions offers coworking space located at 1601 Broadway in New York City, NY. Located in Times Square, this space occupies an entire floor of this beautiful business building. Memberships offer access to 10 hours of conference room time to begin with, access to all of Micro Office&rsquo;s locations, as well as the variety of tools and equipment available--printers, projectors, organizing tools.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><strong><em>Pricing Starting At</em>:</strong> Desk - $495/mo; Private Office - $1,000/mo</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',1,1,'Micro Office Solutions - Time Square'),(77,32,'png','http://www.selectofficesuites.com/','Select Office Suites','<p class=\"p1\">Select Office Suites offers cost-effective office rental options for any size group with an emphasis on providing flexibility. Their turnkey office solutions include furnished private offices, office suites, team rooms, and open workspaces accommodating groups from 1 to 100 people or more. This coworking space promotes an&nbsp;environment where people can work together and build relationships while still enjoying their own space.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><strong><em>Pricing Starting At</em>:</strong>&nbsp;Varies</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',1,1,'Select Office Suites'),(78,26,'png','http://www.neuehouse.com/tagged/thespace','NeueHouse','<p>A private membership work collective intended for both solopreneurs and those leading teams of up to 10 people, NeueHouse is a complete rethinking of the ideal working environment for today&rsquo;s creators in such fields as film, design, fashion, publishing, the arts and tech. NeueHouse is designed for the way creative, dynamic companies operate today.</p>\r\n<p><strong><em>Pricing Starting A</em>t:</strong>&nbsp;Varies</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',NULL,1,'NeueHouse'),(79,31,'jpeg','http://www.qnscollective.com/','QNS Collective','<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">This space offers a collaborative workspace, event and education destination where members make connections, get creative, build with like-minded entrepreneurs, and get work done. Their modern, comfortable environment, designed with productivity in mind and supported by a state-of-the-art infrastructure, assures everyone is well equipped to meet the needs of their diverse membership and unique projects. The large open work space features dedicated desks, private suites, and communal tables.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><strong><em>Pricing Starting At</em>:</strong> Desk - $285/mo; Private Office - $500/mo</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',NULL,1,'QNS Collective'),(80,35,'png','http://www.starkofficesuites.com/locations/new_york_city_office_space/','Stark Office Suites','<p>Stark Office Suites&rsquo; Midtown Manhattan executive suites reflect the highest standards of excellence. Discreet, courteous, and well-qualified support staff. Tasteful d&eacute;cor and a sophisticated business atmosphere. State-of-the-art technology and fiber optic service offerings. And a business community that supports collaboration, networking, and success.</p>\r\n<p><strong><em>Pricing Starting A</em>t:</strong>&nbsp;Varies</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',NULL,1,'Stark Office Suites'),(81,24,'png','http://jaysuites.com/','Jay Suites','<p>Jay Suites is a modern full-service business center providing fully-furnished luxurious office space to its clients. Their vision is to transform the business center industry by committing an unprecedented amount of attention to design, service and quality. As a family-owned business, they pride themselves on the personal attention and support that they can give to every one of their customers. Jay Suites has locations by 34th street, Penn Station, Grand Central, Time Square and the Financial District.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><em>Pricing Starting A</em>t:</strong>&nbsp;Varies</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',NULL,1,'Jay Suites'),(82,34,'jpeg','http://www.thefarmsoho.com/','The Farm','<p>Located in SoHo, The Farm is NYC\'s most engaged community of designers, developers, social change agents, artists, thought leaders and entrepreneurs that have converged to share ideas, innovate and learn in a collaborative and nurturing environment. We all come from an understanding that what we can accomplish together as a community, far exceeds what we can ever hope to accomplish on our own.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><em><strong>Pricing Starting At:</strong></em><strong>&nbsp;</strong>Communal Desk $250/mo; Dedicated Desk $400/mo</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',NULL,1,'The Farm'),(83,58,'jpeg','https://www.wework.com/locations/new-york-city/gramercy','WeWork - Gramercy','<p>WeWork\'s new location on the southeast corner of 23rd and Park. WeWork is the community of creators. They transform buildings into beautiful collaborative workspaces and provide infrastructure, services, events and technology so their members can focus on doing what they love.</p>\r\n<p><em><strong>Pricing Starts At:</strong></em><strong>&nbsp;</strong>Pricing Varies</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',NULL,1,'WeWork - Gramercy'),(84,30,'jpeg','http://www.projective.co/','Projective Space','<p>Projective Space is a coworking space for high-caliber startups, entrepreneurs, and innovators that choose to build their companies in NYC. They provide communal and dedicated workspaces in open plan layout that fosters collaboration between their members.</p>\r\n<p><em><strong>Pricing Starting At:</strong></em> Non-fixed Desk $455 / Fixed-Desk $555 all inclusive</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',1,1,'Projective Space'),(85,33,'jpeg','sotechiespaces.com','SoTechie Spaces','<p>SoTechie space is located at 28 West 29th Street. SoTechie is a leader in the coworking frenzy! With locations in NYC and Cincinnati, our ever-expanding network has serviced hundreds of startups since opening in 2010. The energy that lives within our walls allows for social, uplifting and above all professional engagements. Innovation rests in the creative minds of entrepreneurs&nbsp;seeking exposure. collaboration results in the promoting of ideas. Community driven towards the creation of opportunities. Get KNOWN here! Business mavens, find all the tools you need at SoTechie. Space provides meeting rooms, events spaces and coworking areas. Dreams are shared, milestones are attained, and achievements are forever more withing grasp.</p>\r\n<p><em><strong>Pricing Starting At:</strong></em><strong>&nbsp;</strong>$299 - $399/mo</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',1,1,'SoTechie Spaces'),(91,50,'jpeg','http://www.virgobc.com/midtown-east/','Virgo Business Centers - Midtown East','<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: #777777; font-family: lato, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">575 Lexington Avenue is situated in the heart of Manhattan\'s prestigious Midtown East \"Fortune 500\" corridor. Just steps away are some of New York\'s most prominent office buildings and hotels. This glass-clad office building boasts an award-winning lobby that is sure to make a lasting impression on your guests and clients. This 40,000 square-foot Midtown East office space facility occupies the entire 4th floor and boasts 102 modernly-furnished offices and team rooms.&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: lato, arial, sans-serif; text-shadow: none; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: #777777;\"><em style=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit;\"><strong style=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit;\">Pricing Starting&nbsp;At:</strong></em>&nbsp;$1,000/mo</span></div>','coworking@trumanjames.com',NULL,1,'Virgo Business Centers - Midtown East'),(87,34,'jpeg','www.spark-labs.co','Spark Labs','<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 23.2000007629395px; font-family: lato, arial, sans-serif; color: #777777; text-shadow: none;\">Located in Union Square, Spark Labs is a 5,000 sqft space that has grown into a collective of NYC\'s most exciting tech startups. We can get a tech company up-and-running in less than 24 hours. We\'ll also connect them to the NYC Tech community though our weekly events while providing all the support they need from legal, accounting, recruitment, software &amp; hosting.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 23.2000007629395px; font-family: lato, arial, sans-serif; color: #777777; text-shadow: none;\"><em><strong>Pricing Starting At:</strong> </em>Desk- $350</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',NULL,1,'Spark Labs'),(88,49,'jpeg','http://www.virgobc.com/','Virgo Business Centers - Midtown','<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 23.2000007629395px; font-family: lato, arial, sans-serif; color: #777777; text-shadow: none; text-align: left;\">Our office space locations boast a striking decor and feel, that will leave a lasting impression on our clienteles\' guests and clients. All of our locations are just steps from some of New York\'s most prominent office buildings and hotels. Our furnished office spaces are designed for companies that want to cut costs while maintaining flexibility. Our office come fully , are immediately available, and have flexible terms.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 23.2000007629395px; font-family: lato, arial, sans-serif; color: #777777; text-shadow: none; text-align: left;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 1; font-family: inherit;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 1; font-family: inherit;\">Pricing Starting At:&lt;/s','coworking@trumanjames.com',NULL,1,'Virgo Business Centers - Midtown'),(89,7,'jpeg','http://cowork.rs/gowanus/','Cowork|Rs - Gowanus COMING SOON!','<p>Cowork|Rs\' newest location at 68-92 3rd St. in Gowanus, Brooklyn - COWORK|RS offers you a ready-made community with the potential for collaborations with dynamic people working on cool projects. The organizational setup takes care of the practical stuff&ndash;so you don&rsquo;t have to. The space is bright and comfortable, and makes challenging work easy and fun. The layout encourages random conversation between members to spark ideas, solve problems and collaborate. Their staff works directly with members to support your business needs and make important connections. This location also has a rooftop for events and lounging. Reach out to us for early-access.</p>\r\n<p><em><strong>Pricing Starting At:</strong></em><strong>&nbsp;</strong>Desk - $350/mo; Private Office - $700/mo Office</p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',1,1,'Cowork|Rs - Gowanus'),(90,9,'jpeg','http://dumbostartuplab.com/','DUMBO Startup Lab','<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: #777777; font-family: lato, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Authentic, independent coworking for authentic, independent workers. We are conveniently located in the heart of Brooklyn\'s digital district. Our coworking space features abundant natural light and expansive views to inspire creative thinking and big ideas. Work alongside top designers and developers in our bright, open loft. Amazing customer service and a friendly, collaborative community set us apart.</span>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: lato, arial, sans-serif; text-shadow: none; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: #777777;\"><strong><em style=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit;\">Pricing Starting&nbsp;At:</em></strong>&nbsp;Non-dedicated Desk - $249/mo; Dedicated Desk - $429/mo; 4-person workstation - $1,499/mo</span></div>','coworking@trumanjames.com',NULL,1,'DUMBO Startup Lab'),(92,48,'jpeg','http://www.virgobc.com/grand-central/','Virgo Business Centers - Grand Central','<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: #777777; font-family: lato, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">The Chanin Building is one of the most architecturally significant buildings from New York\'s art deco era. Its lobby is connected to Grand Central Terminal, making this Virgo facility one of the most centrally located in its portfolio. In addition to being a major transportation hub, this neighborhood is rich in hotels, restaurants, and catering facilities. This 100-office facility occupies the entire 17th and part of the 16th floors, totalling 35,000 square-feet.</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: lato, arial, sans-serif; text-shadow: none; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: #777777;\"><em style=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit;\"><strong style=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit;\">Pricing Starting&nbsp;At:</strong></em>&nbsp;$900/mo</span></div>','coworking@trumanjames.com',NULL,1,'Virgo Business Centers - Grand Central'),(93,47,'jpeg','http://www.virgobc.com/empire-state-building/','Virgo Business Centers - Empire State Building','<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: #777777; font-family: lato, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">The Empire State Building stands as the most prominent figure in Manhattan skyline. As a business address, it is world famous, and for Virgo Business Centers, it\'s the flagship of our fleet. This 66-office facility boasts panoramic views from the entire 59th floor of this landmark building. The retail levels in the building include amenities such as eateries, banks, USPS, FedEx and a currency exchange kiosk. This 24/7 building posts doormen at every entrance and employs a team of lobby personnel to quickly process guests.</span>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: lato, arial, sans-serif; text-shadow: none; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: #777777;\"><em style=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit;\"><strong style=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit;\">Pricing Starting&nbsp;At:</strong></em>&nbsp;$1,000/mo</span></div>','coworking@trumanjames.com',NULL,1,'Virgo Business Centers - Empire State Building'),(94,52,'jpeg','http://www.virgobc.com/penn-station/','Virgo Business Centers - Penn Station','<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: #777777; font-family: lato, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">14 Penn Plaza is centrally located in the heart of Manhattan\'s Garment District. Its close proximity to Penn Station makes it convenient to all city commuters. This 82-office facility occupies the entire 9th floor of the building, totaling approximately 27,000 square feet. The surrounding neighborhood&nbsp;includes an abundance of shopping, dining, and entertainment, including the world-famous Madison Square Garden one block from this Virgo location 255 W 34th Street.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px; text-shadow: none; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: lato, arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #777777;\"><em style=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit;\"><strong style=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit;\">Pricing Starting&nbsp;At:</strong></em>&nbsp;$1,000/mo</span></span></span></div>','coworking@trumanjames.com',NULL,1,'Virgo Business Centers - Penn Station'),(95,51,'jpeg','http://www.virgobc.com/midtown-south/','Virgo Business Centers - Midtown South','<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: #777777; font-family: lato, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Located at 304 Park Ave South, this Flatiron District Midtown South Office location is situated in one of Manhattan\'s most vibrant business submarkets. The 30,000 square-foot facility is located on the 10th &amp; 11th floors of this building. Many of the major employers in this neighborhood are in creative industries, which gives the surrounding area a unique flavor. Clients at this location enjoy its proximity to public transportation and some of the most popular restaurants in NYC.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px; text-shadow: none; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: lato, arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #777777;\"><em style=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit;\"><strong>Pricing Starting </strong>At:&nbsp;</em>$450/mo</span></span></span></div>','coworking@trumanjames.com',NULL,1,'Virgo Business Centers - Midtown South'),(97,39,'jpeg','http://www.teemcw.com/','TEEM Coworking','<p>Located at 1463 5th Ave in Harlem, TEEM is a CoWorking community for creative and professional individuals. We strive to break away from the typical office to offer a setting that facilitates effortless networking in a collaborative environment. Within our&nbsp;community,&nbsp;you can meet other like-minded and passionate individuals to expand your ideas and materialize your vision.<br /></p>','coworking@trumanjames.com',NULL,1,'TEEM Coworking'),(98,42,'jpeg','http://harlemgarage.com/','The Harlem Garage','<div style=\"widows: auto; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: #777777; font-family: lato, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Harlem Garage is a coworking space for Harlem&nbsp;businesses&nbsp;and a community space for Harlem. Entrepreneurs work and meet clients in our space, and teams make ideas happen in our collaborative areas. The real magic happens when our members collaborate and network together, and we help make this happen by partnering with local schools and organizations to host networking events, classes, and community events in the space.</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"widows: auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; text-shadow: none; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: lato, arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #777777;\"><em style=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit;\"><strong style=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit;\">Pricing Starting&nbsp;At:</strong></em>&nbsp;Desk - $300/mo</span></span></span></div>','coworking@trumanjames.com',NULL,1,'The Harlem Garage');
